Package: vp
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: SDL-based image viewer for X and console
 Image viewer based on SDL that reads and displays a wide variety of formats.
 Features include fullscreen and windowed modes, arbitrary pan and zoom,
 slideshow, an on-screen filename display, navigation through a list of
 images, operation in both X and the console, and fetching images over
 http and (when built with OpenSSL) https, with redirect following.
